{"tid":583192,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加可以準備回國教大巴黎了...","createTime":"2018-03-06T21:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T10:45:38.000Z","uid":16320,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"39da0e591d4e8c4b1ebe62815fb5edcfb574de7e","tid":583192,"uid":16320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46541835a24df7ff8e86f97c229fd5899b6c1627","tid":583192,"uid":581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:11:37.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺唔會離開阿仙奴"},{"pid":"983f08fa21e5d4f5e2841aaf56db7b102e57810d","tid":583192,"uid":16320,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:03:17.000Z","msg":"真係有風吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n據《每日鏡報》報導，目前雲格在阿仙奴的帥位已經搖搖欲墜，儘管他決心要在兵工廠執行完合約，但是據Football.London報導，巴黎聖日耳門隊有意請這位68歲的老帥。<br />\n<br />\n　　最近，兵工廠遭遇4連敗，其中還輸給厄斯特鬆德和白禮頓這樣的弱隊，這讓阿仙奴球迷不能忍。目前雲格和阿仙奴的合約還剩1年到期，但是大巴黎已經十分有意讓雲格成為他們的下一任教練。<br />\n<br />\n　　然而，雲格卻堅持說，他是那個可以讓情況扭轉的人，有報導稱，他已經告知了自己教練組的成員，他不會在今夏主動辭職。<br />\n<br />\n　　大巴黎方面，在他們被皇馬淘汰出歐冠盃比賽後，現任教練艾馬利可能在今夏離開。法國媒體Le10 Sport也報導稱，大巴黎主席納賽爾又重燃了對雲格的興趣，他已經試圖聯繫雲格，看他是否願意在下季執教PSG。"},{"pid":"f1ec31f8ea92de0200ebe9a091d07f033e49cf22","tid":583192,"uid":50359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:23:44.000Z","msg":"Paris Saint-Germain have reportedly made contact with Arsene Wenger about the 68-year-old succeeding Unai Emery as manager, amid rumours the Frenchman will leave Arsenal this summer. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4efc3e96e35b3744a0e94c6eb390162c5d3225","tid":583192,"uid":3003,"